file_content.text: Apologies--Sergeant Kayen is waiting on the results from these tests.
You have the venom glands? Sergeant Kayen told me to expect you...
Yes, this should be enough for the anti-venom. If I can finish the work in time, the victims will survive.
Thank you. I will tell Sergeant Kayen and our patients what you've done.
Please excuse me--there's very little time, and I must complete the anti-venom.
